Interactive "Choose Your Own Adventure" Game
Project Report

Student Name: Ashumendra Pratap Singh
Course: B.Tech CSE Core
University: VIT Bhopal University
Year: 2029
 
Abstract
This project presents an advanced interactive adventure game developed using Python. The game allows users to explore multiple story paths, manage health, collect inventory items, and experience random events. The project demonstrates fundamental Artificial Intelligence concepts such as intelligent agents, decision-making, and state space representation.
Introduction
Interactive games are an engaging way to learn programming and AI concepts. This project creates a text-based adventure game where players make decisions that influence the storyline and outcomes.
